# SSL Certificate Placeholder
#
# Place your SSL certificates here:
#   - fullchain.pem  (certificate + intermediate chain)
#   - privkey.pem    (private key)
#
# These files should NOT be committed to git.
# Add them manually on the server or use a secrets manager.
#
# For Let's Encrypt certificates:
#   - fullchain.pem is typically at /etc/letsencrypt/live/yourdomain/fullchain.pem
#   - privkey.pem is typically at /etc/letsencrypt/live/yourdomain/privkey.pem
#
# For internal CA certificates:
#   - Request from your organization's IT/Security team
